### Get Dashboard Stats (Total Companies + Top Commodities + Monthly Volume)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/companies/stats
Accept: application/json

### Get Company List (Paginated)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/companies
Accept: application/json

### Get Company List with Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/companies?limit=10&offset=0
Accept: application/json

### Get Company List - Page 2
GET http://localhost:3000/api/companies?limit=10&offset=10
Accept: application/json

### Get Company Detail (replace with actual company name)
# Note: Company names with spaces need URL encoding
GET http://localhost:3000/api/companies/{{companyName}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Existing Shipments Endpoint (for reference)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/shipments
Accept: application/json
